OL,3,C'We've got to listen to the community'
OL,4,C- one year since the Cwmtillery
OL,5,Clandslip
OL,7,FFurther investigations are continuing
OL,8,Fand Councillor Tommy Smith emphasised
OL,9,Fthe need to include residents' voices
OL,10,Fin the process:
OL,12,F"We are working with engineers and
OL,13,Fofficers to understand what further
OL,14,Fwork can take place at the tip, and
OL,15,Fthat may involve re-profiling of the
OL,16,Ftip in the future," he confirmed. "We
OL,17,Fhave got to listen to the community
OL,18,Fgoing forward and take onboard their
OL,19,Fconcerns."
