OL,3,C'We've got to listen to the community'
OL,4,C- one year since the Cwmtillery
OL,5,Clandslip
OL,7,FSince that day, around 800,000 homes
OL,8,Fin Wales have been signposted to
OL,9,Fadvice about disused coal tips as the
OL,10,FWelsh Government continues inspecting
OL,11,Fpotentially dangerous sites.
OL,13,FThere are 2573 recorded coal tips in
OL,14,FWales. 368 are in the highest
OL,15,Fcategories of risk - Category C and D
OL,16,F- and are classed as those with the
OL,17,Fpotential to impact public safety.
